Jewellery ERP & Girvi Management Platform

Girvi Core Module Specification v1.0

Module Code: MOD-GIRVI
Priority: Critical MVP
Version: 1.0
Frontend: Flutter + BLoC
Backend: NestJS
Dependencies: Customer Module, Interest Engine, Vault Module, Compliance Module, Notification Module, Audit Module, Sync Module

⸻

1. Module Purpose

The Girvi Module is the primary revenue-generating module of the platform.

It manages the complete lifecycle of a pledged jewellery loan from customer onboarding to redemption or auction.

The module is responsible for:

* Jewellery Evaluation
* Gold/Silver Valuation
* LTV Calculation
* Girvi Contract Creation
* KFS Generation
* Vault Assignment
* Partial Payments
* Interest Calculation
* Renewals
* Redemption
* Auction Management
* RBI Compliance
* Maharashtra Compliance

