5. Core Business Rules

BR-GIRVI-001

Customer must exist before Girvi creation.

BR-GIRVI-002

At least one item mandatory.

BR-GIRVI-003

At least one photo per item mandatory.

BR-GIRVI-004

Vault assignment mandatory before activation.

BR-GIRVI-005

KFS acknowledgement mandatory before disbursement.

BR-GIRVI-006

Redeemed Girvi cannot be edited.

BR-GIRVI-007

Auctioned Girvi cannot be edited.

BR-GIRVI-008

MCX Rate becomes immutable after contract creation.

