SCR-022 Valuation & LTV

Purpose

Calculate loan eligibility.

⸻

Inputs

Net Weight
Purity
Gold Rate
Silver Rate

⸻

Valuation Formula

Fine Gold Weight:

Fine\ Gold\ Weight = Net\ Weight \times \frac{Carat}{24}

⸻

Valuation:

Valuation = Fine\ Gold\ Weight \times Gold\ Rate

⸻

LTV Formula

LTV = \frac{Loan\ Amount}{Valuation} \times 100

⸻

RBI Rules

Loan Amount	Max LTV
≤ ₹2.5L	85%
₹2.5L–₹5L	80%
> ₹5L	75%

⸻

Validation

Hard block above limit.

Owner override required.

